name: VETTR AI
description: VETTR AI is an analytics platform on Solana that uses artificial intelligence to detect and track new meme tokens in real time. The system monitors on chain data and alpha channels, selects newly active tokens, and scores them using models trained on thousands of historical signals. Each alert includes key metrics such as market cap, liquidity, holder distribution, smart money activity and simple risk checks so that users can review the data before making their own trading decisions. The VETTR token is a Solana based utility asset that connects the analytics product with its community. Holding the token grants access to premium features.
